<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="block-vt">block <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /blɒk/    美 /blɑːk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>堵塞；阻挡；妨碍：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When we saw the road blocked with snow, we decided to spend the holiday at home. 
当我们看到大雪堵塞道路时，就决定在家过这个假期了。</p><footer> 2013 北京</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The building has windows with a coating that blocks heat while letting in light.
这座大厦的窗户有一种涂层，可以让光线进来而把热量阻挡在外。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Someone is blocking our plan. 
有人在妨碍我们的计划。</p></div></div>